---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="container footer-inner">
    <div class="col">
      <span class="mono section-label">Updates</span>
      <p class="muted">
        新着の旗艦記事と機種レコードを通知します。<br />
        <em>※ 購読フォームは仕上げ段階で接続予定（Buttondown 等）。</em>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col">
      <span class="mono section-label">Follow</span>
      <ul class="links">
        <li><a href="#" rel="me">X / Twitter</a> <span class="muted">（準備中）</span></li>
        <li><a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a> <span class="muted">（準備中）</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col">
      <span class="mono section-label">Contact</span>
      <ul class="links">
        <li><a href="/contact">相談・お問い合わせ</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container colophon">
    <span class="mono">© {year} Deploid /toB</span>
    <span class="mono muted">Built with Astro · Cloudflare Pages</span>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin-top: 6rem;
    padding-block: 3rem 1.75rem;
    background: var(--bg);
  }
  .footer-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  .col p,
  .col ul {
    margin: 0;
  }
  .links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .muted {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }
  em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .colophon {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .footer-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .colophon {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
